{
  "id": "adv_love_2603_01_01",
  "title": "Episode 1 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_companyoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimisyouzi",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――社会人一年目の春",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1800.0000158
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "真面目に自己紹介する",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 143.0999980768
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh007.m4a",
              "text": "本日から配属になりました\n長所は真面目でコツコツ頑張れることです\nご指導ご鞭撻のほどよろしくお願いします！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 143.0999980768,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio004.m4a",
              "text": "50点。肩に力が入り過ぎ\n言ってることも無難で印象に残らないわ\nでも、実直なところは嫌いじゃないわよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 151.2333314102,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "ウケを狙う",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 162.3666647435
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh008.m4a",
              "text": "自己紹介します！\nあれ～？\nこのキーボード、Gを押しても反応しないぞ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 162.3666647435,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh009.m4a",
              "text": "G、故障かい！\nじー、こしょうかい……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 169.0666647435,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio005.m4a",
              "text": "……ふーん",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 174.7333314102,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "俺は仕事でミスをしたのか！？",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "俺、何かミスをしましたか！？\nすみません！　すぐにやり直します！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 221.100006215,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_stm-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 226.1666728816
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio008.m4a",
              "text": "ミスだなんて一言も言ってないでしょ\n何をそんなに焦ってるのよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 226.1666728816,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "いや、その……\n神崎先輩は厳しい人だと聞いていたので\nてっきり叱られるのかと……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 231.600006215,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio009.m4a",
              "text": "その風評被害はやめてもらえないかしら\n私は必要な指摘をしているだけで\n怒っているつもりはないから",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 239.100006215,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio010.m4a",
              "text": "まあ、他の人よりも多少\n口調は厳しいかもしれないけど……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 247.5666728816,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "（自分が厳しい自覚はあるんだ……）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 252.900006215,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "配属初日から残業させる気か！！",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "いくらなんでも、新入社員に初日から\n残業させるのはまずいと思います",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 255.9666728816,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 261.000006215
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh019.m4a",
              "text": "それはパワハラです！　ブラック企業です！\nそんなことをしたら\n労働組合が黙っていませんよ！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 261.000006215,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio011.m4a",
              "text": "私をなんだと思ってるのよ\n配属初日から残業なんてさせる訳ないでしょ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 266.9999919734,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "飲みに行く",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 280.8333253068
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh020.m4a",
              "text": "分かりました\nお供します、神崎先輩！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 280.8333253068,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio013.m4a",
              "text": "神崎先輩って呼び方も堅苦しいわね\n私のことは名前呼びでいいわ\n同僚はみんなそう呼んでるから",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 284.1999919734,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh021.m4a",
              "text": "いいんですか？　じゃあ……莉央さん\n改めて、よろしくお願いします",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 293.2666586401,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh022.m4a",
              "text": "（厳しいところもあるけど\n仕事が出来て面倒見がいい、いい先輩だよな\n莉央さんとのサシ飲み……少し楽しみだ）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 300.5665853979,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio014.m4a",
              "text": "じゃあ、行きましょうか\n天動さんと鈴木君も準備は出来てるわね？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 311.4999187312,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 5766.733693899994
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rui003.m4a",
              "text": "はい、いつでも出発出来ます",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 317.1665853979,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "鈴木",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-suzuki007.m4a",
              "text": "お供させていただきます！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 319.6332866511,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh023.m4a",
              "text": "えっ、瑠依？　鈴木？\nどうして二人までついて来るんだ？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 321.7999533178,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rui004.m4a",
              "text": "どうしても何も、先輩達が開いてくれる\n新人歓迎会に、新入社員の私達が\n出席するのは当たり前じゃない",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 326.4332866511,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh024.m4a",
              "text": "新人歓迎会！？\n莉央さんと二人きりじゃなかったのか……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 334.6999533178,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio015.m4a",
              "text": "あら、そんなに私と二人で飲みたかったの？\nだったら、早く仕事で認められることね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 340.3332866511,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-rio016.m4a",
              "text": "貴方が仕事で一人前になったら\nその時は、私から飲みに誘ってあげるわ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 348.3999533178,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh025.m4a",
              "text": "（一人前になったら、か……\nよーし、莉央さんに認められるように\nこれからバリバリ頑張るぞ！）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 354.9999533178,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "誘いをきっぱり断る",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh026.m4a",
              "text": "俺は行きません\n第一、上司が部下を飲みに連れ回すなんて\nパワハラで問題になりますよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 364.6999533178,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 371.5332866511
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_01_01-koh027.m4a",
              "text": "飲みニケーションなんて昭和の遺物です\n今は個人の時間を大切にする時代なんです",
